{"tid":1300123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺學聯半收皮之後學界反而靈活咗","createTime":"2019-07-09T09:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T11:13:39.000Z","uid":207710,"like":102,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3e5aa42884c86ad56691c28ee98185f334034a1e","tid":1300123,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"以前學聯年代主要得八間成員院校參與社運<br />\n好多議題例如六四悼念咁根本唔同院校唔同立場<br />\n變相捆綁式表態好難<br />\n宜家學界講嘢多數係一串院校聯署咁款<br />\n八大以外嗰啲大專院校參與度高咗<br />\n又唔使話次次統一立場先做嘢<br />\n有時得五六間院校已經開聲<br />\nG20示威嗰次又可以唔同院校唔同做法<br />\n諗返轉頭退聯令學界社運避免咗行禮如儀嘅抗爭<br />\n令學界更加融入羣衆而唔係起大臺<br />\n當初退聯真係估唔到有呢個結果"},{"pid":"7ece782d6d2ecf21ae514f89b6847efbeaf8fb48","tid":1300123,"uid":263161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:19:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96ee4d7e8aeaac0e573971aa7a231daab0b1698a","tid":1300123,"uid":264172,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"中共一定好後悔攪散左學聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3027b448ec6fa01fe646724acaf62f5ae71c31d","tid":1300123,"uid":164050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14e2eec31dc165edd3c4b5c2b4709b5bd1aecaa1","tid":1300123,"uid":55271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"當年學聯有份搞死雨革<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cd5f51a8a1070746110575b37500f15e6e1d9a","tid":1300123,"uid":164050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa0748a34fb6c1b53e098bd21ebde5284ba01081","tid":1300123,"uid":207710,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b3027b448ec6fa01fe646724acaf62f5ae71c31d","tid":1300123,"uid":164050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"