","tid":1300123,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b05f3cb557755072e6f149232451f5cdd06f9ef","tid":1300123,"uid":207710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:30:06.000Z","msg":"不過最可惜係學聯啲物業同錢無得分餅仔畀啲退聯院校<br />\n喺嗰度攞錢反送中我諗仲好過喺學生會庫房攞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:00:35.000Z","msg":"學聯d物業慢慢搞啦<br />\n之前搞個自治8樓都拖勁耐先搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9000694787d796260985f6613d5cde683a4f0d","tid":1300123,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5335a97cab8f0ef960179e0fecdc4474201bf5b3","tid":1300123,"uid":122994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁梗係啦，學聯以前行共識制。<br />\n<br />\n即係要小組討論到全部院校都同意某一方案為止先可以出學聯名黎做。連小數服從多數都唔係<br />\n<br />\n所以學聯既決策慢到仆街，而且決出黎既方案一定係妥協出黎，即係唔會係最激既方案<br />\n<br />\n另外就係好易滲透。只要一間院校有鬼，佢就可以拖到成個學聯做唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前同學聯中人辯論既時候佢地會話：雖然係咁，但都唔洗退架，有咩行動想做咪自己做囉。我話有樣野叫大台效應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"大台將群眾捆綁左, 有少數人即使心清高, 如果想做出同大台相反既決定<br />\n都會俾群眾視為叛逆, 搞到只有服從, 就算你有道理都行動唔到<br />\n大台呢d 模式係以前通訊唔方便先岩用, 而家通訊發達冇理由再俾大台綁住自己雙腳"},{"pid":"46c35ff7c33e07ea6f8549ebb6b1e27ec2897552","tid":1300123,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"群龍無首是大吉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZEise1IHLVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZEise1IHLVw&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7JtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=cbf92d7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZEise1IHLVw</a>"},{"pid":"dfae9212d3d8862b10847b299a1c939bd61ee253","tid":1300123,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:37:19.000Z","msg"